  <li><a rel="external" href="https://twitter.com/chogmceo">Twitter @CHOGMCEO</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="other-information">Other Information</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Born 1962; diplomat since 1983</li>
  <li>Fluent French and Japanese</li>
  <li>Experience in negotiation, running Private Offices, media work, and running a large mission and networks (250 people in France, 4000 in Europe)</li>
</ul>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_4036">
            <h1 id="chief-executive-commonwealth-summit-unit">Chief Executive, Commonwealth Summit Unit</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Tim Hitchens is the Chief Executive of the Commonwealth Summit Unit. He is responsible for delivering the Commonwealth Heads of Government Meeting (CHOGM) 2018, working closely with the Commonwealth Secretariat and member states. His dedicated unit, based in the Cabinet Office, will report directly to the Prime Minister.</p>
</div>
            <div class="read-more">
                <p class="js-hide-other-departments organisations-name-list">
